This is the Debian GNU/Linux prepackaged version of freeciv.

This version of the package was made by Lalo Martins <lalo@webcom.com>, from
sources obtained from:

	ftp://freeciv.ultraviolet.org/pub/freeciv/freeciv-1.7.1.tar.gz
                                        (you may download it .bz2 too)

Earlier versions were maintained by Richard Braakman <dark@xs4all.nl>.

Earlier versions were maintained by Karl Sackett <krs@debian.org>.

For more information see:

	http://www.freeciv.org

